  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on a heartwarming adventure with a fluffy bunny on their path to become the Legendary Easter Bunny! Deliver enchanted eggs to furry friends to help them survive, and build bonds strong enough to rid the forest of the relentless Thrae hunters.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🐰<strong> 2 - 4 hrs of Stress Free Gameplay</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎨 <strong>Craft & Decorate Magical Eggs</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015130/extras/17d74c9a9382a035721d8d7caf1917f2.poster.avif?t=1745347794\" width=616 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015130/extras/17d74c9a9382a035721d8d7caf1917f2.webm?t=1745347794\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015130/extras/17d74c9a9382a035721d8d7caf1917f2.mp4?t=1745347794\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Craft, customize and deliver enchanted eggs to suit each NPC’s needs.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deep customization system with plenty of colors and patterns hidden around the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🌎 <strong>Explore a Diverse Landscapes</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015130/extras/7dd753a28e63af1ceabd46035af41dd0.poster.avif?t=1745347794\" width=616 height=424 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015130/extras/7dd753a28e63af1ceabd46035af41dd0.webm?t=1745347794\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015130/extras/7dd753a28e63af1ceabd46035af41dd0.mp4?t=1745347794\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Journey through vibrant ecosystems, from lush forests to spooky swamp environments.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore every corner of the map to find secret locations, rare resources, and bonus content.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🤝 <strong>Build Relationships and Unlock Rewards</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Form meaningful bonds with 9 Unique NPC's all with different stories to tell and requests.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Interact with a choice driven narrative system that influences your standing within the animal community</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >⚙️ <strong>Outsmart sneaky traps</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015130/extras/2a06449feb22ab796478397fed94a631.poster.avif?t=1745347794\" width=616 height=402 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015130/extras/2a06449feb22ab796478397fed94a631.webm?t=1745347794\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015130/extras/2a06449feb22ab796478397fed94a631.mp4?t=1745347794\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Neutralize traps by using toolkits to lock pick, or solving puzzles.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🧩 <strong>Engaging Puzzles and Challenges</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015130/extras/253011b2a1aa81e90ea71b44e78cb905.poster.avif?t=1745347794\" width=616 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015130/extras/253011b2a1aa81e90ea71b44e78cb905.webm?t=1745347794\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015130/extras/253011b2a1aa81e90ea71b44e78cb905.mp4?t=1745347794\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve puzzles and mini games to unlock new paths, gather crafting materials, and discover hidden secrets.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use creativity and strategy to meet the unique challenges presented by the Thrae.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🌿 <strong>Foraging and Resource Collection</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015130/extras/52cada1da84ee81a9b5e0b5b3027ccfd.poster.avif?t=1745347794\" width=616 height=424 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015130/extras/52cada1da84ee81a9b5e0b5b3027ccfd.webm?t=1745347794\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015130/extras/52cada1da84ee81a9b5e0b5b3027ccfd.mp4?t=1745347794\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Search the world to gather essential resources like berries, twigs, and golden sap to craft magical eggs and quest items.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fish for Metal scraps to help clean the environment and craft tools to remove the Thrae's traps from the region.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🌟 <strong>Uncover the Easter Bunny’s Mysteries</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn the origin of the Easter Bunny and his magical eggs through captivating storylines.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015130/extras/386379ccf951e08e6e877cb4cb2a6f9b.avif?t=1745347794\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎶 <strong>Immersive Visuals and Original Soundtrack</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Delight in a whimsical art style inspired by springtime nature and wildlife.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy an enchanting original soundtrack that combines atmospheric melodies with regional musical influences.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Disclaimer: </strong><i>Thrae</i> explores themes such as death and grief as part of its narrative. These subjects are handled with care and sensitivity to support the emotional depth of the story. If these themes may be difficult for you, please take this into consideration before playing.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on a heartwarming adventure with a fluffy bunny on their path to become the Legendary Easter Bunny! Deliver enchanted eggs to furry friends to help them survive, and build bonds strong enough to rid the forest of the relentless Thrae hunters.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features:</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🐰<strong> 2 - 4 hrs of Stress Free Gameplay</strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎨 <strong>Craft & Decorate Magical Eggs</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015130/extras/17d74c9a9382a035721d8d7caf1917f2.poster.avif?t=1745347794\" width=616 height=328 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015130/extras/17d74c9a9382a035721d8d7caf1917f2.webm?t=1745347794\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015130/extras/17d74c9a9382a035721d8d7caf1917f2.mp4?t=1745347794\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Craft, customize and deliver enchanted eggs to suit each NPC’s needs.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Deep customization system with plenty of colors and patterns hidden around the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🌎 <strong>Explore a Diverse Landscapes</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015130/extras/7dd753a28e63af1ceabd46035af41dd0.poster.avif?t=1745347794\" width=616 height=424 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015130/extras/7dd753a28e63af1ceabd46035af41dd0.web