r Bunny’s Mysteries</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Learn the origin of the Easter Bunny and his magical eggs through captivating storylines.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2015130/extras/386379ccf951e08e6e877cb4cb2a6f9b.avif?t=1745347794\" width=800 height=450 /></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🎶 <strong>Immersive Visuals and Original Soundtrack</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Delight in a whimsical art style inspired by springtime nature and wildlife.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy an enchanting original soundtrack that combines atmospheric melodies with regional musical influences.</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Disclaimer: </strong><i>Thrae</i> explores themes such as death and grief as part of its narrative. These subjects are handled with care and sensitivity to support the emotional depth of the story. If these themes may be difficult for you, please take this into consideration before playing.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
